Package edu.cnm.deepdive.sereknitty.model.dao

Interface RowDao

public interface RowDao
Provides CRUD operations on Row entity instances. CREATE, INSERT, UPDATE, and DELETE operations are implemented as ReactiveX Single tasks, which execute on subscription; some SELECT tasks are implemented using LiveData queries, which execute on observation, or (if already being observed) on Room-based updates to the underlying tables.
